<subsection name="Firewall Configuration">

<p>
To open Solr port (8983), run the following commands
</p>

<source>
firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=8983/tcp --permanent
firewall-cmd --reload
firewall-cmd --zone=public --list-ports
</source>

</subsection>


